<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=euc-kr" />
    <title>12_pop자동차보험설계기본정보</title>
    <!--<link rel="shortcut icon" href="https://direct.hi.co.kr/images/common/favicon.ico"/>-->
    <script language="JavaScript" src="../../js/lib/jquery-1.11.2.min.js"></script>
    <script language="JavaScript" src="../../js/lib/jquery-ui.min.js"></script>
    <script language="JavaScript" src="../../js/lib/jquery-fakeform-0.5.js"></script>
    <script language="JavaScript" src="../../js/common.js"></script>

    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css"  href="../../css/jquery-ui.min.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css"  href="../../css/base.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css"  href="../../css/common.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css"  href="../../css/layout.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css"  href="../../css/content.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css"  href="../../css/popup.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css"  href="../../css/motor.css" />
	<script>
		$(function(){
		    $(".disabledRaioCon input[type=radio]").on("change",function(){
				var target = $(this).closest("li");
				var idx = $(this).closest("li").index();

                $(".disabledRaioCon").find(".inputBase").addClass("disabled");
                $(".disabledRaioCon").find(".inputBase input").attr("disabled", true);
                $(".disabledRaioCon").find(".inputBase input").attr("disabled","");

				target.find(".inputBase").removeClass("disabled");
				target.find(".inputBase input").attr("disabled", false);
				target.find(".inputBase input").attr("disabled","")

			})
		})
	</script>
</head>
<body class="boxType">



<!-- 04_보험료확인_pop특약_마일리지 : s-->
<!--layerPopWrap : s-->
<div class="dim_bg"></div>
<div class="layerPopWrap failjoin w600">
    <div class="titleArea">
        <h2>자동차보험 설계 기본정보</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="popupContentArea">
		<h3 class="infoTit mb15"><span class="fontPoint1">홍길동 고객님,</span> 설계내용 확인 후 차량정보를 입력해주세요.</h3>
		<div class="carInfomation">
			<dl>
				<dt>차량정보 </dt>
				<dd>캠리</dd>
			</dl>
			<dl>
				<dt>차량세부정보 </dt>
				<dd>Camry 2.5 XLE Hybrid</dd>
			</dl>
			<dl>
				<dt>추가부속품</dt>
				<dd>가죽시트,블랙박스</dd>
			</dl>
			<dl>
				<dt>차량등록년도</dt>
				<dd>2017년</dd>
			</dl>
			<dl>
				<dt>운전자범위(최저연령)</dt>
				<dd>부부한정(만28세이상)</dd>
			</dl>
			<dl>
				<dt>지정1인</dt>
				<dd>-</dd>
			</dl>
			<dl>
				<dt>배우자 </dt>
				<dd>홍길순(880716) </dd>
			</dl>
		</div>
		<!--inputTable : s-->
		<div class="inputTable inputBline onlyInput mb10">
			<div class="title inputTitle">
				<h4 class="tit fz15">차량번호 또는 차대번호 입력</h4>
			</div>
			<div class="inputSet">
				<ul class="inputArea inlineBlock disabledRaioCon">
					<li class="item pr20">
						<div class="radio mt8">
							<input type="radio" name="carNumber" id="carNumber1" checked>
							<label for="carNumber1"><span class="fontLevel1">차량번호</span></label>
						</div>
						<div class="inputBase placeholder h40 ml10" style="width: 155px;">
							<input type="text" title="자동차번호" placeholder="자동차번호">
						</div>
					</li>
					<li class="item">
						<div class="radio mt8">
							<input type="radio" name="carNumber" id="carNumber2">
							<label for="carNumber2"><span class="fontLevel1">차대번호</span></label>
						</div>
						<div class="inputBase placeholder h40  ml10 disabled" style="width: 155px;">
							<input type="text" title="자동차번호" placeholder="ex: AAABB1111CC" disabled>
						</div>
					</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>
		<!--inputTable : e-->

		<div class="btnAreaWrap tac mt20">
            <a href="#" class="btn line inlineBlock gray"><span>취소</span></a>
            <a href="#" class="btn line inlineBlock orange"><span>확인</span></a>
        </div>
    </div>
    <a href="#" class="btnClose"><img src="https://direct.hi.co.kr/images/common/btn_popup_close.png" alt="닫기"></a>
</div>
<!--layerPopWrap : e-->
